  "onboardingWelcomeHeadline": "Hi! Here's how Finko works.",
  "onboardingWelcomeIntro": "Finko follows how your money really works: it lives in accounts, moves with every transaction, gets grouped into categories, and budgets help you plan ahead. That's the whole idea.",
