  "onboardingWelcomeCategoriesBody": "Categories tell you what your money was for—groceries, rent, fun. An account is where your money is; a category is what it's for.",
  "onboardingWelcomeBudgetsTitle": "Budgets",
  "onboardingWelcomeBudgetsBody": "A budget is a plan, not a rule. It shows you where to adjust—it's not about winning or losing.",
  "onboardingProfileIntro": "Let's start with the basics to set up your experience.",
  "onboardingAccountsIntro": "Add each place you keep money—bank, cash, cards. Don't worry about being exact; you can edit anytime.",
  "onboardingCategoriesIntro": "Categories group your money by purpose. Remember: an account is where your money is; a category is what it's for.",
  "onboardingRecurringIntro": "Do you have income that arrives regularly? Telling us when and how much lets Finko project your months.",
